latestIgtvVideos.title: Lockdown Engagement
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I know times are tough & the situation is unfavourable, but we gotta hold on to the brighter things. Couldn’t stand the idea of having even a slight dull moment on @sarinabhinav ‘s engagement. 
It didn’t matter if all we had was our home & 16 people, we came together to celebrate life and love. 
Mega props to @sunakshimohindra for being the most chill bride, who never let any amount of last minute changes dampen her spirits. 
Hope you enjoy watching our little but heart filled celebration 🤍

latestIgtvVideos.title: Brush Challenge 💄
Fix You | Coldplay Cover
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
*deep breaths*⁣⁣
⁣⁣
welcome to garden sessions with the Sarin’s! ⁣⁣
never put up something like this on instagram before, so this is very new territory. the lockdown got @sarinabhinav picking up his guitar again after years and it got me singing along, also after a very long time.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
not too sure if we would have recorded anything if it wasn’t for @sunakshimohindra : you already got the love song from our lover boy, so this one’s from me. in my head, you did get married today & you’re family, no matter when the wedding happens ❤️ ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
also people, posting this with sweaty palms, quiet literally, so please be nice to us kids. hope we all can take this time to somehow find peace & bring each other up. sending you all virtual hugs, have a lovely evening! 🌸⁣⁣
⁣
⁣
